short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Just another Google Docs dark mode without all the bull shit

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Just another dark mode extension specifically for Google Docs. This does nothing except insert some CSS on docs.google.com pages. Fuck all those other extensions that record your personal data and track what you do. I don't care about that, I just wanted an extension that works.
